    "name": "Cellulant Tingg Payouts API",
    "description": "Tingg Payouts (Beep Server) \u2014 send value to mobile money wallets, bank\naccounts, airtime/data, and bill payments across 35 African countries\nthrough a single global JSON endpoint.\n\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Cellulant Developer Support\n Email: developer@cellulant.io",
